@startuml Progress Tracking - Sequence Diagram
title Record Progress Measurement

actor User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant Handler
participant Measurement
participant Repository

User -> Frontend: Enter measurements
Frontend -> API: POST /api/progress/measurements
API -> Handler: RecordProgressMeasurementCommand
Handler -> Measurement: Create(userId, date, weight, bodyFat)
Measurement --> Handler: measurement
Handler -> Repository: AddAsync(measurement)
Repository --> Handler: Success
Handler --> API: measurementId
API --> Frontend: 201 Created
Frontend -> Frontend: Update charts

@enduml
